  

Select “All configurations”

![](pics/msvc-settings_html_m37ea733d.png)

  

At “Configuration Properties/General/Character Set” select ”Not Set”

![](pics/msvc-settings_html_33910ae5.png)

  

  

At “Configuration Properties/Debugging/Environment” add “c:\yborm\bin” to your
project's PATH

![](pics/msvc-settings_html_53d3cb51.png)

  

At “Configuration Properties/VC++ Directories/Include Directories” add
“c:\yborm\include\yb”, “c:\yborm\include” and $(ProjectDir)

![](pics/msvc-settings_html_701e5726.png)

  

  

At “Configuration Properties/VC++ Directories/Library Directories” add
“c:\yborm\lib”

![](pics/msvc-settings_html_32f49c2b.png)

  

At “Configuration Properties/C/C++/Precompiled Headers choose not to use this
feature

![](pics/msvc-settings_html_2311dde8.png)

  

  

At “Configuration Properties/Linker/Input/Additional Dependencies” add YB.ORM
libraries and friends:

ybutil.lib

yborm.lib

libxml2.lib

libboost_date_time-vc100-mt-gd-1_46_1.lib

libboost_thread-vc100-mt-gd-1_46_1.lib

  

![](pics/msvc-settings_html_64d1c5b6.png)

  

  

